.TH "SVGAELEMENT.DOWNLOAD" "3JS" "October 21, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
SVGAElement.download \- SVGAElement: download property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]download\f[B]\f[R] property of the \f[CR]SVGAElement\f[R]
interface returns a string indicating that the browser should treat the
linked URL as a download.
.PP
This property can be set, to change the URL\(cqs \f[CR]download\f[R]
value.
It reflects the value of the \f[CR]download\f[R] attribute.
.RS
.PP
\f[B]Note:\f[R] This value might not be used for download.
This value cannot be used to determine whether the download will occur.
.RE
.SH VALUE
A string.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IP \(bu 2
\f[CR]download\f[R] attribute
